description:
Have you ever wondered why the ultimate Hero, Jesus, made such life-altering decisions? Dive into the profound choices Jesus made, not by force but willingly. From leaving the comforts of heaven to enduring a 40-day wilderness fast and facing the perils of public ministry, discover the sacrifices Jesus embraced out of pure love for you and me.#Shorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ #YouTubeShorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​

To watch the full video, paste this link into your browser: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bZv6XjrURJE&feature=youtu.be
